                            <h1 className="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 tracking-tight">Lindy Party<br />?좎껌?섍린</h1>
                            <p className="text-gray-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                                醫뗭? ?щ엺?ㅺ낵 ?④퍡?섎뒗 ?밸퀎?????<br />
                                吏湲?諛붾줈 ?쒖옉?대낫?몄슂.
